---
title: Roasted Squash, Ricotta and Bacon Risotto with Fried Sage
description: Looking for the perfect vegetarian dish for date night? This beautiful risotto is the one for you. It's creamy, sweet and oh-so-easy! Roasted butternut squash, blistered tomatoes and crispy sage are here to make date night dreams come true. Don't let "risotto" intimidate you, this dish is mostly hands-off.
